These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, amaryllis, begonia, sunflower, rose
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, july, february, march, january
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person who growspoppy##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person drinking tea is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who growsrose##2
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
13. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | almond-milk | tea     | coffee   | lemonade |
| Flower   | begonia     | amaryllis      | sunflower | rose   | poppy    |
| Birthday   | march  | july     | june | february | january  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

