.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, dunhill, swisher, bolivar, siglo
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
5 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, monopoly, billiard, go
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person playing backgammon and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the dunhill-smoker##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the person playing monopoly is the swisher-smoker##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Cigar         | bolivar | chaman | siglo    | dunhill  | swisher    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Game   | go   | bridge     | backgammon    | billiard  | monopoly     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

