.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
5 different pets are kept: pony, fish, ferret, hedgehog, cat
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, roller, airplane, taxi
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the owner of the fish##1
 2. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the trike is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
13. the person driving the taxi is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
| Pet   | ferret      | fish      | hedgehog       | cat       | pony       |
| Transport         | quad-bike | taxi  | airplane    | trike    | roller        |

