.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, onion, papaya, tomato, watermelon
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, golf, rowing, skiing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, old-henry, dannemann, swisher, siglo
 1. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person eating tomato##2
 5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is rowing is the prince-smoker##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
13. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | watermelon  | papaya     | tomato   | onion     | artichoke |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking    | singing  | skydiving | puzzles   |
| Sport   | basketball        | badminton    | skiing     | golf     | rowing    |
| Cigar   | old-henry    | dannemann | swisher | siglo | prince   |

