.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: folk, salsa, country, rock, funk
There 5 different types of food: apricot, broccoli, lettuce, orange, watermelon
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, lawyer, manager, social-worker, writer
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis, zinnia, lily, aconite
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 3. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 4. the fan of country is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person eating apricot##2
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 7. the fan of rock is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | funk       | folk   | country      | salsa    |
| Food       | watermelon | orange        | apricot       | lettuce       | broccoli |
| Job        | writer     | lawyer        | social-worker | dancer        | manager  |
| Flower      | lily | zinnia | azalea      | aconite | amaryllis  |

