 3. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 4. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the french##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the fan of house is between the owner of the horse and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the dog is on the right of the french##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the horse and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the fan of country is on the right of the polish##1
13. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
