.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, mirinda, soy-milk
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, lily, daisy, balloon-flower, iris
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball, sailing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: gospel, classical, techno, funk, ambient
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the fan of classical and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 7. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the fan of techno is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who growsdaisy##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Flower       | iris | zinnia | daisy  | balloon-flower | lily    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Music-Genre   | funk       | techno      | ambient      | gospel | classical  |

