.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
There are 5 different favourite colors: amber, ebony, black, white, mauve
House: tower, colonial, craftsman, farmhouse, art-deco
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, hip-hop, house, trance
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the colonial house##1
 2. the person who likes white is between the craftsman house and the person who likes black##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the person who likes white##1
 4. the art-deco house is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the tower house is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person who likes mauve and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
10. the person who likes amber is on the right of the craftsman house##1
11. the person who likes black is the colonial house##1
12. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Color           | ebony | black | white | mauve    | amber  |
| House   | farmhouse  | colonial    | tower | craftsman    | art-deco |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | blues        | ambient   | house    | trance     |

