.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: papayad-games, chess, photography, puzzles, skydiving
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, october, september, august, june
5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
There 5 different types of food: orange, papaya, onion, cherry, corn
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person eating corn##1
 4. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's birthday is in march and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person eating orange and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is papayad-games##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's hobby is papayad-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is papayad-games is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | photography | puzzles   | chess      | papayad-games |
| Birthday   | march   | august    | october | june | september      |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goldfish    | cat       | lizard     | mouse      |
| Food     | onion | corn        | orange  | papaya        | cherry    |

