.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
5 different games are played: snooker, bridge, billiard, monopoly, canasta
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, electronic, reggae, rock
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower, iris, daffodil, tulip
 1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person who growsdaffodil and the fan of rock##2
 3. the fan of rock is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the fan of ambient is between the person who growstulip and the fan of electronic##2
 6. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is the fan of blues##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is the fan of blues##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Game         | billiard    | canasta  | bridge  | snooker      | monopoly |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | ambient    | rock    | reggae       | blues         |
| Flower   | daffodil  | bellflower | tulip    | iris     | balloon-flower      |

 